data.title: Margaret Elizabeth Casey Desmond Snudo Lamprecht Steggf (1892
data.meta_description: She was first married to John Henry Desmond  (b. ca. 1886 ).  * * * *   She is mentioned in the following article about her friend:  * * * * *  SUSASNE ALLEN (upper photo), French model found dead in her apartment, and  Mrs. Margaret Lamprecht, (lower photo),  Meanwhile the Identity of Lc Gros Baboon (the big baboon)...
